prompts.frontCover:
Greeting card front cover, a whimsical and funny dreamy fantasy scene featuring cartoon illustrated versions of Jordan and Lao Lao from the reference photo. The setting is a surreal, magical landscape where their favorite things come to life. In the background, there's a snowy mountain range made of fluffy white rice, with soy sauce rivers flowing down its slopes. Instead of trees, there are giant stalks of broccoli and bok choy.

In the mid-ground, Jordan is playfully snowboarding down a slope of perfectly seared wagyu steak, kicking up a spray of binary code (0s and 1s) instead of snow. He is wearing his navy blue t-shirt. Lao Lao, wearing her white zip-up top, is sitting nearby on a giant piece of salmon nigiri sushi, laughing and cheering him on. She holds a pair of oversized chopsticks.

Floating gently around them are various magical food items: shrimp dumplings drifting like clouds, sushi rolls (maki) orbiting them like tiny planets, and glowing Chinese lanterns shaped like takeout boxes. The whole scene is bathed in a soft, ethereal glow with pastel colors and magical sparkles.

Centered on the card, in a clear area, is the text "Happy Birthday, Jordan!" written in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script. The overall style is flat 2D vector art, charming, and filled with humorous, personal details.
